    <item>
      <title>苹果禁止《堡垒之夜》制作者制作欧盟应用商店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/epic-games-says-apple-has-terminated-developer-account-in-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司已阻止 Epic Games Inc. 在欧洲为 iPhone 用户开设自己的应用程序商店，这家《堡垒之夜》制造商表示，此举是对其批评这家科技巨头以及违反该地区全面新反垄断规则的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/epic-games-says-apple-has-terminated-developer-account-in-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:59:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Teleperformance 将人工智能视为 Klarna 恐慌之后的增长机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/teleperformance-sees-ai-as-growth-opportunity-after-klarna-panic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[呼叫中心巨头 Teleperformance SE 否认了上周股价暴跌后生成人工智能可能扰乱其核心客户服务业务的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/teleperformance-sees-ai-as-growth-opportunity-after-klarna-panic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:51:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>推动出售的立法者表示，TikTok 可以继续保持“糟糕的口型同步”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/tiktok-can-keep-its-bad-lip-sync-lawmakers-pushing-a-sale-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[支持一项迫使 TikTok 的中国母公司出售这款视频共享应用程序的法案的立法者周三努力表明，他们无意摧毁这个受欢迎的平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/tiktok-can-keep-its-bad-lip-sync-lawmakers-pushing-a-sale-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果在抛售 2000 亿美元后看起来是多年来最超卖的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/apple-looks-most-oversold-in-years-after-200-billion-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，苹果公司在 2024 年处境艰难，最近的疲软使得该股看起来像是多年来最严重的超卖。]]></description>
